        "WDD_ITEM_SPEAR_NAME": "Spear of the Seven Dark Flames of the Night's Eclipse, Forged by the Gods Under the Watch of Ten Thousand Honored Knights. Receive This Item to Wield Untold Powers Beyond All Others.",
        "WDD_ITEM_SPEAR_PICKUP": "Deal 1 more damage.",
