        "WDD_ITEM_SPOPE_NAME": "Spope",
        "WDD_ITEM_SPOPE_PICKUP": "Massively increase your damage, <style=cDeath>BUT exit the game when you are hit.</style>",
        "WDD_ITEM_SPOPE_DESC": "Increase your damage by <style=cIsDamage>{0}%</style> <style=cStack>(+{0}% per stack)</style>. <style=cDeath>Exit the game when you are hit.</style>",
        "WDD_ITEM_SPOPE_LORE": "We knew the world would not be the same.\n\nA few people laughed. A few people cried. Most people were silent.\n\nI remembered the line from the Hindu scripture the Bhagavad Gita. Vishnu is trying to persuade the prince that he should do his duty, and to impress him takes on his multi-armed form, he says:\n\n'Now I am become spope, the destroyer of worlds.'\n\nI spose we all thought that, one way or another.\n\n<style=cStack>- J. Rogert Spopenheimer, inventor of the Spope</style>",

        "WDD_ITEM_MOONWEED_NAME": "Moon Weed (Weed from the Moon)",
        "WDD_ITEM_MOONWEED_PICKUP": "Multiply all of your items' activation chance, <style=cDeath>BUT your camera rotates on hit. Critical strikes 'Critically Rotate' in the other direction.</style>",
        "WDD_ITEM_MOONWEED_DESC": "<style=cIsDamage>Multiply the proc coefficient of all your attacks by {0}%</style> <style=cStack>(+{1}% per stack)</style>. <style=cDeath>Your camera rotates</style> {2} <style=cStack>(+{2} per stack)</style> degree(s) on hit. On <style=cIsDamage>'Critical Strike'</style>, your camera <style=cDeath>'Critically Rotates'</style> {3} <style=cStack>(+{3} per stack)</style> degrees in the other direction.",
        "WDD_ITEM_MOONWEED_LORE": "DON'T EVER BUY NO WEED FROM THE LUNAR BAZAAR BRO.\n\n<style=cStack>- Mithrix</style>",

        "WDD_ITEM_GAMBLER_NAME": "1-800-522-4700",
        "WDD_ITEM_GAMBLER_PICKUP": "<style=cDeath>All nearby chests are converted into chance shrines.</style> On pickup, gain a set of profitable items.",
        "WDD_ITEM_GAMBLER_DESC": "<style=cDeath>All nearby chests are converted into chance shrines.</style> On pickup, gain one stack each of <style=cShrine>Roll Of Pennies</style>, <style=cShrine>Ghor's Tome</style>, and <style=cShrine>Chance Doll</style>. <style=cDeath>If you lack the DLC for any of these items, you must get on</style> <style=cShrine>Stake.com</style> <style=cDeath>and win enough to buy it.</style>",
        "WDD_ITEM_GAMBLER_LORE": "'You have a problem.'\n\n'I don't have a problem. I have a solution. That solution is betting on red, and the problem I'm solving is our mortgage payments.'",

